;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fapps 的免费应用程序。 microsoft.com%2Fdetail%2F9pjgrcldlx5v%3Fhl%3Den-US%26gl%3DUS&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F7%2F17%2F24200294%2Fmicrosoft-designer- app-launch-windows-ios-android-features&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Windows&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ microsoft-designer/id6448308247&quot;>;iOS&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.microsoft.designer&amp;amp;hl=en_GB&quot;>;Android&lt; /a>;.该移动应用程序包含创建图像并随时随地编辑图像的功能。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图像：Microsoft&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Microsoft Designer 编辑器视图。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;IVs0I4&quot;>;Microsoft Designer 包括常用的文本提示...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200294/microsoft-designer-app-launch-windows-ios-android-features&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200294/microsoft-designer-app-launch-windows-ios-android-features" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200294/microsoft-designer-app-launch-windows-ios-android-features</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-17T11:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-17T11:00:00-04:00</updated><title>凯迪拉克为其汽油动力凯雷德 (Escalade) 增添了电动汽车的光芒</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt =“2025凯迪拉克凯雷德”src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/dcFO8Md5YVLFzS4D7sSiN777CC4=/443x0:7481x4692/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/73465920/Escalade_V_21284_V9.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：凯迪拉克&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;OQ68xh&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023 /8/9/23822742/cadillac-escalade-iq-ev-reveal&quot;>;凯迪拉克 Escalade IQ&lt;/a>;，该汽车制造商的游艇大小的豪