tly-approval/&quot;>;将这一许可描述为“巨大的飞跃”培育肉类行业的进步。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;H7zWbB&quot;>;“宠物父母迫切需要一种更好的方法来喂养他们的猫和狗肉，”Meatly 首席执行官欧文·恩索尔 (Owen Ensor) 在一份声明中表示，他表示该公司培育的宠物食品将使他们能够“以对我们的星球和其他动物更加友善的方式”做到这一点。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;8vR5Sp&quot;>;Meatly 表示计划推出其首款产品的商业样品...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 7/17/24200412/uk-lab-grown-cultivated-meat-pet-food-approval-meatly&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200412/uk-lab-grown-cultivated-meat-pet-food-approval-meatly" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200412/uk-lab-grown-cultivated-meat-pet-food-approval-meatly</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-17T10:30:30-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-17T10:30:30-04:00</updated><title> 2024 年亚马逊 Prime Day 最佳 Apple 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;木桌上 Apple Smart Folio 中的第 10 代 iPad。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/oYdIb7z8DV-6HI8huMdjGTvSJJg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73463853/226361_Apple_iPad_10.9_10th_gen_ DSeifert_0004.5。 jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;最新款 iPad 价格降至历史最低价。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Dan Seifert / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Q3NbJ3&quot;>;感谢亚马逊 Prime Day，您无需等到今年的黑色星期五即可在苹果产品上节省大笔费用。尽管是亚马逊的活动，但令人惊讶的是，一些最优惠的商品包括流行的苹果产品，从高端 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized/dp/ B0D1XD1ZV3/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;最新 AirPods Pro&lt;/a>; 到入门级 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp /B0D1WXVQTN/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;第三代 AirPods&lt;/a>; — 两者均创下历史新低价格。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;5zdx1Z&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以获得的最佳亚马逊 Prime Day 科技优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24197967/amazon-prime-day-best-tech- Deals-gadgets-2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2024 年亚马逊 Prime Day 指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24191617/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals -guide-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;k8ggOU&quot;>;不仅 AirPods 获得大幅折扣，&lt;a href=&quot; https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Smartwatch-Midnight-Aluminum-Resistant/dp/B0CSVB8BP1?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;spoken noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 9&lt;/a >;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BJLCWFNM?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;最新 iPad&lt;/a>; 以及其他优秀的苹果设备。下面，我们汇总了其中的精华，以便您更轻松地了解这些交易。如果您对 Apple 生态系统之外的优惠感兴趣，请&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24197967/amazon-prime-day-best-tech-deals-gadgets-2024&quot;>;查看我们的主要 Prime Day 综述&lt;/a>;，让您节省更多。&lt;/p>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;rQtJh3&quot;>;最佳 AirPods 优惠&lt;/h2>; &lt;div id=&quot;ujoQU2&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component =&quot;productcard:12375646&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;ul>;&lt;li id=&quot;2vyjUK&quot;>;通常为 549.99 美元，...&lt;/li>;&lt;/ul>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/24196778/amazon-prime-day-apple-deals-airpods-watch-ipad-macbook-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24196778/amazon-prime-day-apple-deals-airpods-watch-ipad-macbook-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24196778/amazon-prime-day-apple-deals-airpods-watch-ipad-macbook-2024</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-17T10:11:01-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-17T10:11:01-04:00</updated><title>诉讼称，OpenAI 首席执行官山姆·奥尔特曼 (Sam Altman) 价值 2700 万美元的豪宅是一个泳池漏水的“柠檬”</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Sam Altman 的照片拼贴画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/a-m3CEeF_m4ADuH0d69Fvv-9oTs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73465804/STK201_SAM_ALTMAN_CVIRGINIA_B.0。 jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge； Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Slrnip&quot;>;山姆·奥尔特曼 (Sam Altman) 在旧金山的价值 2700 万美元的豪华住宅显然存在问题，从漏水的无边泳池到有故障的管道将未经处理的污水倾倒到房产上。根据&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/24828536-lombard-st-lawsuit?responsive=1&amp;amp;title=1&quot;>;一项诉讼&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https ://sfstandard.com/2024/07/16/sam-altman-lawsuit-lemon-mansion/?utm_source=twitter_sitebutton&quot;>;&lt;em>;旧金山&lt;/em>;&lt;em>;标准&lt;/em>;链接&lt;/ a>; 前往 OpenAI 首席执行官的住所，该住所声称 Altman 购买了“普遍存在粗制滥造和偷工减料”的“柠檬”。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Fy7dEh&quot;>;这栋 9,500 平方英尺的庄园位于旧金山弗朗西斯科标志性的朗伯德街，在这里可以俯瞰城市和海湾。正如您在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hGkVxIyKnEA&quot;>;房屋概览&lt;/a>;中所看到的，它的一些主要功能包括一个四面无边泳池，悬挂在房子的边缘，一个通向车库的“蝙蝠洞”，以及一个使用回收雨水灌溉的系统......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200354/sam-altman-san-francisco-mansion-lawsuit-lemon-openai&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200354/sam-altman-san-francisco-mansion-lawsuit-lemon-openai" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200354/sam-altman-san-francisco-mansion-lawsuit-lemon-openai</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>